title: Rent to Own in Pearland!
posting_body: ['Ready to own but not ready for a mortgage?', 'Lease a house while you prepare for a mortgage, and buy it back at any time.', 'Pick the house of your choice and have up to 3 years to buy it back!', 'Hello!', "I'm a local realtor who specializes in Divvy rent-to-own homes.", 'Contact me to learn more about this amazing program that lets you get into a home and on the way to homeownership.', 'If interested, you MUST MEET *ALL* qualifications:', '$0 Application Fee!', '550+ credit score or higher', '$40,000+ annual income from 2 co-applicants', 'Employed at least 3 months', 'No bankruptcies or evictions in the past 12 months', 'Only a 1-2% down payment is needed', 'This amazing program helps you save because 25% of the Rent goes towards a down payment!!', "If this isn't the home you'd like you can pick almost any home for sale.", 'Please send a text message or click the link below to learn more about this incredible opportunity.', 'Grant Rogers', 'show contact info', 'Winhill Advisors Kirby', '<URL>']
